My heartbeat is becoming a big brother and turning TWO 🤍 

You gave me purpose. You have changed me. You saved me. You are my strength. You give me joy. I can’t believe you will be TWO in a couple of days and a big brother in less than 2 months. My mommy heart can’t take it. I love you endlessly.

TWO. 

I can’t believe you are TWO. I get so emotional about time flying but I cherish every single milestone. 

I have always dreamed of having a mamas boy and you are more than I could ever dream of. 

Got knew I needed you. Your love is endless. You are my heartbeat. I love you with everything in me.  Today and everyday is all about you bookie 🤍
